Dino Game (Pygame Edition)

A simple yet polished recreation of the classic Chrome Dino game built using Python and Pygame.
The project demonstrates game loops, object-oriented design, collision detection, and basic animation systems.

Features
Smooth player movement and jumping physics
Random cactus obstacles
Flying bird enemies with animation
High score system (saved locally)
Dynamic day/night cycle with smooth transitions
Sound effects (jump, death, scoring)
Sprite animation for player and birds
Increasing challenge through timed obstacle spawning
Tech Stack
    Python 3.x
    Pygame
📁 Project Structure
project/
│
├── assets/              # Game images (Dino, Bird, Ground, etc.)
├── sounds/              # Sound effects (jump, die, point)
│
├── obstacles/
│   ├── cactus.py        # Cactus enemy logic
│   └── bird.py          # Bird enemy logic
│
├── player/
│   └── player.py        # Player (Dino) class
│
├── setting.py           # Game configuration (WIDTH, HEIGHT, FPS)
├── main.py              # Main game loop
└── highscore.txt        # Stores highest score locally


▶️ Installation & Running
1. Install dependencies
pip install requirements.txt
2. Run the game
python main.py

🎮 Controls
Key	Action
SPACE	Jump
SPACE (Game Over)	Restart Game
ESC / Close Window	Quit Game

🧠 Game Architecture

The game is built around a main game loop that runs continuously:

Event Handling
    Keyboard input
    Window events
Update Phase
    Player physics (gravity, jumping)
    Obstacle spawning and movement
    Collision detection
    Score tracking
    Day/Night transitions
Render Phase
    Drawing background
    Rendering player and obstacles
    Displaying score and UI
🏆 Scoring System
    Score increases over time while surviving
    High score is saved locally in highscore.txt
    Automatically updates when a new record is achieved
🌗 Day & Night Cycle
    Background smoothly transitions between light and dark states
    Creates a dynamic visual experience during gameplay
🚧 Obstacles
    🌵 Cactus: Ground-based obstacle
    🐦 Bird: Flying obstacle with random height variation

Each obstacle is spawned dynamically to increase difficulty over time.

